thread.title: HILARY
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by HILARY

author: HILARY
title: HILARY
text:
We've been using Redspot Car Rentals for most of our interstate travels and have not been disappointed!
Staff were friendly and helpful, quick transition from the airport to the car, and quick turnaround in terms of car return/drop off prior to the flight.
All in all, a great experience, and would certainly recommend!
